data.description:
Welcome home to this 4 bedroom Colonial located right off of Lake Erie! Location, location, location!! You are 2 minutes from 2 parks
located on the lake!! Both Century Park in Lorain and Lakewood Beech Park in Sheffield Lake are perfect for taking the kids, hanging
out or just relaxing and enjoying the views!! Your oversized kitchen includes a nook area for a small pub table, extra pantry area or as
a mud room coming in off of the back of the house....What ever you decide!! You will love the new porcelain tile floors, granite
counters and tile backsplash!!! On the 2nd floor you have your recently update bathroom with new porcelain floors, porcelain tub
surround and all new fixtures!! 3 bedrooms on the 2nd floor and a huge 17 x 11 4th bedroom on the 3rd level!! Your waterproofed
basement is equipped with a half bath and is waiting for your finishing touches! Enjoy peaceful evenings on your fully enclosed front
porch or in your mostly fenced in back yard which is perfect for entertaining! All appliances stay so all you have to do is MOVE IN!!!
